- `docs/architecture/DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` — TypeORM 엔티티·ERD·필드 설명·Enum. DDL: `docs/db/schema.sql` (전체 SQL: `docs/db/`)
- `docs/architecture/API_SPECIFICATION.md` — **전체 API 엔드포인트 명세 (서버↔모바일 매핑)**
